com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.common

Class TimeRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.common.TimeRecord

  • public class TimeRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores time information. This class along with TimeRecordQueue are used to collect individual time differences for statistical calculation in a thread-safe manner -- one thread can store information by adding to the records queue and another can retrieve the information from the records queue and do any desired calculation.
